BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (These tiny acts didn't seem like much, but the mirror had shown her   even small) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (kindnesses create big feelings in others.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (Every single interaction was a chance to make the world a tiny bit better.) Tj ET
