BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 21) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Sometimes, Zara messed up. She was still human, after all.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Sometimes she said something without thinking and saw the hurt flash across someone's) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (face.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (But the difference now was that she NOTICED. She felt it. And she fixed it immediately.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td ('I am sorry. That came out wrong. What I meant to say was...' became one of her most-used) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (phrases.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (And people always forgave her because they knew she genuinely cared about their feelings.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td ([Illustration: Zara catching herself after saying something thoughtless, immediately) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (apologizing with sincerity, the other person's expression softening from hurt to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (understanding]) Tj ET
