BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 22) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (So here's what Zara learned   and what she wants YOU to know:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (You have more power than you think. Every word you say and every thing you do affects the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (people around you.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (You can make someone's day wonderful or terrible   with just one sentence, one action, one) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (choice.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (So before you speak, before you act, ask yourself the Golden Rule question:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td ('Would I want someone to treat ME this way?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (If the answer is yes   go ahead. If the answer is no   choose differently. It really is) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 578.2 Td (that simple.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td ([Illustration: A child looking directly at the reader with kind eyes and an open) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td (expression, a golden glow around them representing the power they have to affect others) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 526.4 Td (positively, empowering and warm]) Tj ET
endstream
