BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Here is your Golden Rule challenge:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Tomorrow, before every single thing you say or do, pause for ONE second and ask: Would I) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (want this done to me?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (Before you tease someone   pause. Before you ignore someone   pause. Before you grab) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (something first   pause.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (Just one second of thinking can change everything. One second turns a hurtful moment into) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (a kind one.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (Try it for one day. Then try it for a week. Then watch your whole world transform, just) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 578.2 Td (like Zara's did.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td ([Illustration: A child pausing before speaking, a small golden clock showing one second,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td (the moment of choice between kindness and unkindness, choosing the golden path]) Tj ET
