BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (And remember: the Golden Rule is not just about being nice. It is about SEEING people.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Seeing when someone is lonely. Seeing when someone is hurt. Seeing when someone needs a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (friend.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (You do not need a magic mirror to do this. You just need to pay attention.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (Look at the people around you   really look. What do they need? What would YOU need in) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (their shoes?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (The answer to that question is always the right thing to do. Always.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td ([Illustration: A child looking around their classroom or playground, truly SEEING the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (people around them   noticing who is lonely, who is hurt, who needs a friend   with a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (gentle golden glow of awareness around them]) Tj ET
endstream
