BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 25) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (The Golden Rule is the oldest rule in the world. Every culture, every religion, every wise) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (teacher has taught it.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (Treat others as you want to be treated. It is that simple. And it is that powerful.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (One person using this rule can change a classroom. A classroom can change a school. A) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (school can change a town.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (And you? You are that one person. Start today. Start now.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (The mirror is in your heart. The gold is in your hands. The rule is yours to live.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td ([Illustration: A golden rule emblem glowing in a child's heart, ripples of golden light) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (spreading outward to their classroom, their school, their community, showing how one) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (person changes everything]) Tj ET
endstream
