BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (The Moral of the Story) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Treat Others as You Want to Be Treated) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.4 Td (Zara discovered that every action has a ripple. When she was mean, everyone around her) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.4 Td (became mean. When she was kind, everyone became kind. The Golden Rule is the most powerful) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.4 Td (rule in the world: treat others the way YOU want to be treated. Before you speak, imagine) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.4 Td (those words being said to you. Before you act, imagine someone doing that to you. If it) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.4 Td (would hurt you, don't do it to others. If it would make you happy, go ahead and spread) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 576.4 Td (that joy! You have the power to change your whole world   one kind action at a time.) Tj ET
endstream
